---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Human-in-the-loop Review | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="Human-in-the-loop AI workflows that keep expert judgement central to high-value decisions."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Human-in-the-loop Review
      </p>

      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        AI workflows that keep experts in control.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI designs AI systems where human judgement, review, and accountability remain central to evidence-heavy and high-consequence work.
      </p>

      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">The problem</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            AI should support expert judgement, not bypass it.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            In policy, infrastructure, regulation, health, energy, and investment decisions, outputs must be reviewed, challenged, and interpreted by people who understand the context.
          </p>
          <p>
            Human-in-the-loop review ensures that AI assists the workflow while experts retain control over judgement, quality, and final decisions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">What it supports</p>
        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          Review points built into AI-assisted work.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Expert review</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Keep analysts, advisers, and domain experts responsible for reviewing AI-assisted outputs.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Structured workflows</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Embed AI within repeatable workflows that include review, approval, and quality-control steps.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Evidence checking</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Support verification against source material, model outputs, references, and approved evidence.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Decision accountability</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Ensure that AI contributes to decisions without obscuring who reviewed and approved the advice.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">Example applications</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Designed for work where quality control matters.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Review of AI-assisted research, evidence synthesis, and policy summaries.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Quality assurance for modelling outputs, assumptions, and decision reports.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Controlled workflows for sensitive client, public-sector, or regulatory material.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Governance of AI-assisted advice before publication, submission, or decision use.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Keep expert judgement at the centre of AI-assisted decisions.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about human-in-the-loop review, quality assurance, and governed AI workflows.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
